<template>
    <hooper>
        <slide>
            slide 1
        </slide>
        <slide>
            slide 2
        </slide>
        ...
    </hooper>
</template>

<script>
import { Hooper, Slide } from 'hooper';
import 'hooper/dist/hooper.css';

export default {
    name: 'slidBar',
    components: {
        Hooper,
        Slide
    }
};
</script>

<style>
.slid-bar {
    margin-top: calc(var(--nav-hieght) + 10px);
}
</style>
